text: The inhibitory effects of Abies koreana Horstmann's Silberlocke essential oil, mainly constituted by bornyl acetate, limonene and Î±-pinene, on pro-inflammatory mediators (NO and PGE 2 ) were related to the modulation of iNOS and COX-2 expression, since the expression of iNOS and COX-2 mRNA and iNOS and COX-2 protein was reduced [143] .
